title: Unique 1 Bed / 1 Bath w/ Private Entrance in Westwood. Close to UCLA!
posting_body: ['Unique 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath Apartment With Private Entrance!', 'This apartment is unique with its own private entrance, features include a large patio, wood flooring throughout, and central air conditioning.', 'Kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, a gas stove/oven, a dishwasher and a refrigerator.', 'Nestled North of Wilshire Blvd., you are in close proximity to UCLA, UCLA Medical Center, and Century City.', 'Treat yourself to everyday conveniences immediately outside your front door like Whole Foods, Ralphs, Target, Trader Joe’s, and the weekly Farmers Market.', 'Call us today at', 'show contact info', '!', 'visit our website at <URL>.', '972 Hilgard Avenue', 'Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024', 'This 1 bedroom apartment offers the following amenities:', 'Private Patio', 'Granite Countertops', 'Tile Bathroom And Kitchen Floors', 'Disability Access', 'Microwave', 'Gas Stove/Oven', 'Extra Storage', 'Mirrored Closet Doors', 'Private Entrance', 'Dishwasher', 'Refrigerator', 'Central Air And Heating', 'Wood Flooring', 'Covered Parking', 'Disclaimer: Pictures are a representation but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Advertised unit availability, rental rates, and terms are updated every 24 hours and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please call for latest availability details.']
